title: Teacher Assistant Interview
Application Type: I applied online. I interviewed at Emmanuel (Klang) in May 2017
Interview Descriptions: first email/ phone call: to send you the date and venue of the interview-> classroom physical experience: having class with the children->1 to1 interview: to understand more about you-> email confirmation: reject/accept
Interview Questions: Do you think you are really able to commit despite the tough situation

title: M&E Consultant Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 2 weeks. I interviewed at Emmanuel (Liberia, Cundinamarca) in Mar 2017
Interview Descriptions: The interview process was very effective and less stressful, I was contacted after applying through this site. An interview date was fixed and conducted. The process was very accommodative.
Interview Questions: I was asked about my key experiences and practice
